<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />He does wonderful things that will be remembered;</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh is gracious and merciful.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />He gives food to his faithful followers.</para>

<para style="q1">He will always call to mind his covenant.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />He showed his powerful works to his people</para>

<para style="q1">in giving them the inheritance of the nations.</para>
